@page "/"

<PageTitle>Learning Hub</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to the Learning Hub</h1>

<p class="lead">
    A small sample site to explore lessons and courses. Use the sidebar to navigate.
</p>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Get started</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Browse curated courses and bite-sized lessons to practice Blazor and web concepts.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="courses">View courses</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Quick lessons</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Short, focused lessons you can open right away.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="lessons">Open lessons</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h5>Featured lesson</h5>
        <div class="border rounded p-3 mb-2">
            <h6>Introduction to Components</h6>
            <p>Learn how to create and compose Blazor components, pass parameters, and handle events.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary" href="lesson/1">Open lesson</a>
        </div>

        <h5>Mini exercises</h5>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="counter">Try the Counter sample</a> — practice events and state.</li>
            <li>Experiment with styles in <code>wwwroot/css/app.css</code>.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>